  This map shows the countries where the State Department has established a regional environmental hub. There are 12 hubs, each located in the U.S. embassy in that country.&nbsp;   
However, these hubs do not only cover the country they are based in, but instead work to advance environmental issues in several countries within their region. &nbsp; 
